<bibRefCitation author="Perez Goodwyn" box="[284,547,314,338]" firstAuthor="Perez Goodwyn" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" pagination="1 - 71" refId="ref67536" refString="Perez Goodwyn, P. J. (2006) Taxonomic revision of the subfamily Lethocerinae Lauck &amp; Menke (Heteroptera: Belostomatidae). Stuttgarter Beitrage zur Naturkunde, Serie A (Biologie), 695, 1 - 71." type="journal article" year="2006">Perez Goodwyn (2006)</bibRefCitation>
